<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Login | ITShirt.dev</title>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no" name="viewport">
    <%= favicon_link_tag asset_path("favicon.png"), rel: "icon", type: "image/x-icon" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag :application_administrator, media: "all" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
    <meta name="google" content="notranslate">
  </head>
  <body class="<%= yield :body_class %>">
    <%= render "shared/flash" %>
    <div class="unauthenticate__left">
      <div class="intro-banner">
        <div class="intro-banner__img">
          <img src="<%= asset_path("agency.png")%>">
        </div>
        <div class="intro-banner__text">
          <h1>#{Code} & Life</h1>
          <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Adipisci provident culpa maiores ex veniam quaerat, veritatis tempore officia laborum qui distinctio suscipit ullam? Ipsa sapiente quas repellat nam facere. Doloribus.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="unauthenticate__right">
      <%= yield %>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
